  <title>Electrical diagrams</title>

  <para>This section includes circuit diagrams for all the vessel's
  distribution cabinets and panels.</para>

  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="4">
      <thead>
        <row>
          <entry>Distribution cabinet</entry>

          <entry>Type</entry>

          <entry>Location</entry>

          <entry>Function</entry>
        </row>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>DC1</entry>

          <entry>24VDC</entry>

          <entry>Battery compartment (galley)</entry>

          <entry>Main DC distribution cabinet. Battery connection, charging,
          inverting and distribution.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C1</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Lower deck lobby</entry>

          <entry>Main AC distribution cabinet. Power circuits for guest cabin,
          office, day head, lobby and galley.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C2</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Lower deck lobby</entry>

          <entry>Lighting circuits for guest cabin, office, day head, lobby
          and galley. Intruder alarm.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C3</entry>

          <entry>24VDC</entry>

          <entry>Master cabin</entry>

          <entry>NMEA interface. Fore-locker and mast equipment.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C4</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Saloon</entry>

          <entry>Lighting and power circuits for master cabin, en-suite and
          saloon.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C5a</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Engine room</entry>

          <entry>Engine room equipment AC supplies.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C5b</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Engine room</entry>

          <entry>Engine room equipment AC control interface.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C5c</entry>

          <entry>24VDC</entry>

          <entry>Engine room</entry>

          <entry>NMEA interface. Engine room DC services.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>C6</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Fore locker</entry>

          <entry>Lighting and power for fore locker.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Main engine interface</entry>

          <entry>24VDC</entry>

          <entry>Engine room</entry>

          <entry>Engine - helm control panel connection.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Thermal store interface</entry>

          <entry>230VAC</entry>

          <entry>Engine room</entry>

          <entry>Thermostat, heat exchanger and boiler control.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Domestic panel</entry>

          <entry>24VDC</entry>

          <entry>Lower companionway</entry>

          <entry>Ship's master panel</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

